{
  "page": "Argos Sevenstar",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Argos Sevenstar</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Weeping_Water\" title=\"Weeping Water\">Weeping Water</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Argos Sevenstar</b> was an <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> warlord.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Argos_Sevenstar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Argos was one of many warlords during the <a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">coming of the Andals</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>. He led the great of the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> threats to the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>, but was smashed by an alliance between King <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Stark\" title=\"Theon Stark\">Theon Stark</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">House Bolton</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Weeping_Water\" title=\"Battle of the Weeping Water\">Battle of the Weeping Water</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the aftermath of victory, King Theon raised his own fleet and crossed the <a href=\"/index.php/Narrow_sea\" title=\"Narrow sea\">narrow sea</a> to the shores of <a href=\"/index.php/Andalos\" title=\"Andalos\">Andalos</a> in western <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>, with Argos's corpse lashed to the prow of his flagship. Theon's <a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">northmen</a> burned a score of villages, captured three tower houses and a fortified <a href=\"/index.php/Sept\" title=\"Sept\">sept</a>, and put hundreds to the sword. When he returned to the north, the Hungry Wolf planted the heads of the slain on spikes along his coasts as a warning for other potential invaders.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Argos_Sevenstar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The North: The Kings of Winter.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403220023\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.068 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.263 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 464/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10418/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3388/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 544/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1018/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.47 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  255.416      1 -total\n 96.69%  246.951      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.80%  244.700      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.59%   29.604     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  2.71%    6.923      2 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.20%    5.627      2 Template:Ref\n  1.30%    3.315      2 Template:Ref/core\n  1.03%    2.619      1 Template:References\n  0.40%    1.028      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18513-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403220023 and revision id 331899\n -->\n",
